OL,3,CEvents cancelled at farm shop after
OL,4,Cparasite outbreak
OL,6,FA farm shop in Cowbridge has cancelled
OL,7,Fevents after an outbreak of an
OL,8,Fintestinal parasite.
OL,10,FHealth authorities are investigating a
OL,11,Fnumber of cases of Cryptosporidium
OL,12,Finfection in people who attended calf
OL,13,Fand lamb feeding and petting sessions
OL,14,Fat Cowbridge Farm Shop, Marlborough
OL,15,FGrange Farm, Cross Ways, Cowbridge
OL,16,FCF71 7LJ.
OL,18,FThere are 28 cases currently
OL,19,Fassociated with this incident.
