OL,4,Cparasite outbreak
OL,6,FSu Mably, Consultant in Health
OL,7,FProtection at Public Health Wales said
OL,8,F"We would advise anyone who has
OL,9,Fvisited the farm, particularly those
OL,10,Fwho attended feeding or petting
OL,11,Fsessions, and who is now experiencing
OL,12,Fsymptoms to contact their GP.
OL,14,F"Symptoms typically begin between two
OL,15,Fand 10 days after contact with the
OL,16,Fparasite and can last for up to two
OL,17,Fweeks.
